casebody.data:
A. H. D’Alemberte, G. W. Ward, J. R. Wells, Tom Shuler, J. F. Shuler, Milton Pledger and C. D. Clark, Petitioners, v. John W. Malone, Judge of the Second Judicial Circuit of Floida, and Dannett H. Mays, Respondents. Petition for Prohibition. (Supreme Court of Florida, En Banc, October 20, 1908.) Reeves & Watson for petitioners.

Original proceeding by petition for Prohibition filed by petitioners and dismissed on praecipe of attorneys for petitioners.
